 Its field of view is only 350 meters 

00:01:44.300 --> 00:01:47.400
 Although the armor of the Soviet chariot is better than the French chariot 

00:01:47.500 --> 00:01:50.100
 Plus its main gun - BL-9 

00:01:50.200 --> 00:01:55.800
 It can cause up to 488 damage in one shot, and only the US T34 can outperform it! 

00:01:57.600 --> 00:02:00.367
 Of course, we have to mention the armor of IS-3, although the thickness of the armor is not amazing. 

00:02:00.467 --> 00:02:05.167
 But its well-known arrow-shaped front armor is very effective. 

00:02:05.267 --> 00:02:08.933
 Its turret armor is also one of the best in its class. 

00:02:10.133 --> 00:02:11.700
 So, what kind of tank turret armor is the thickest? 

00:02:11.800 --> 00:02:13.100
 T32! 

00:02:13.200 --> 00:02:15.400
 In general, this chariot is quite balanced. 

00:02:15.500 --> 00:02:20.400
 It has a field of view of 400 meters, a good elevation angle and a good aiming time. 

00:02:20.500 --> 00:02:22.500
 The fly in the ointment is the lack of flexibility 

00:02:22.600 --> 00:02:27.567
 American tanks are much slower than other tanks, but this is very important. 

