00:02:41.100 --> 00:02:44.267
 It seems to be the perfect chariot in the dream... but this is just an illusion 

00:02:44.367 --> 00:02:46.700
 In fact, its mobility is very low 

00:02:46.800 --> 00:02:51.733
 Coupled with lower armor penetration, poor field of view and poor radio range, it makes it less 

00:02:51.833 --> 00:02:55.533
 So in general, this chariot is not really necessary on all maps. 

