 Another chariot that is worth mentioning when talking about team battle is T34. 

00:03:00.267 --> 00:03:03.433
 Its single shot damage and armor penetration are very good 

00:03:03.533 --> 00:03:06.600
 Its turret armor is second only to T32 

00:03:06.700 --> 00:03:08.933
 And it has a good elevation angle 

00:03:09.033 --> 00:03:11.467
 However, these are the only ones that are only a bit 

00:03:11.567 --> 00:03:15.533
 Because it has a slower rate of fire and lower damage per minute 

00:03:15.633 --> 00:03:17.167
 Its body armor is very weak 

00:03:17.267 --> 00:03:20.900
 Its flexibility is close to T32, but a little bit worse 

00:03:23.433 --> 00:03:28.033
 Another Soviet heavyweight, the KV-4, is very similar to the gold coin chariot of its class. 

00:03:29.000 --> 00:03:32.433
 Excellent armor and durability, but the field of view is very poor 

00:03:32.533 --> 00:03:40.367
 Due to poor flexibility and low damage per minute, you will find that this tank is less suitable for team combat mode than KV-5. 

00:03:41.267 --> 00:03:43.933
 Chinese chariots are also worth mentioning 

00:03:44.033 --> 00:03:46.867
 Chinese tanks are very similar to IS-3 

00:03:46.967 --> 00:03:51.867
 Their durability levels are very close, but the field of view and damage per minute are better. 

00:03:51.967 --> 00:03:56.100
 The flexibility of 110 and 112 is close to that of the Soviet Union. The highest speed of Chinese tanks is higher. 

00:03:56.400 --> 00:04:02.467
 However, due to the low thrust, their acceleration is worse than IS-3. 

00:04:02.567 --> 00:04:05.167
 Therefore, the flexibility is also poor 

00:04:05.267 --> 00:04:10.367
 In addition, you can operate the turret very efficiently when driving the IS-3, which is very important for team operations. 

00:04:10.467 --> 00:04:14.533
